<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="continuous-adj">continuous <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kən'tɪnjuəs/    美 /kən'tɪnjuəs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>连续的；持续的；延伸的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a continuous noise
持续不断的噪音</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The rain has been continuous since this morning.
从今天早上开始到现在雨一直下个不停。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>continuously /kən'tɪnjuəsli/ adv   </p></div>